title: Jungling help.
body:
Hey everyone!
I've just reached level 30 and I'm just smashing norms for the time being as I want to learn how to be a good jungler. I consistently vs silvers/golds/plats in norms (if that even means anything). Just wondering if you could link me good vids or just give good tips.

Champs I play:
Shyvana
Vi
Warwick

I'm going to buy:
Lee Sin
Zac
Evelynn
Elise.

I'm pretty much new to jungling, as I preferred mid up to level 25. Even the real basics would probably help me. Champ suggestions are appreciated as well! 

Thanks in advance.

replies.body: hmu, if you need coaching fam
I'm an Evelynn one-trick, so if you need any help with her (mechanics, build, pathing), I'd be happy to help :D
